"{\"uid\": \"capital.ba-the-municipality-of-istocni-stari-grad-donates-land-worth-three-million-bam-to-jahorina-olympic-centre\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"ISTO\\u010cNI STARI GRAD - The significantly underdeveloped Municipality of Isto\\u010dni Stari Grad has donated nearly 70 dunums of land worth three million BAM to the \\\"Jahorina\\\" Olympic Centre for the construction of \\\"the largest toboggan run in the Balkans\\\".\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 249, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 18, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isto\\u010dni_Stari_Grad\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"ISTO\\u010cNI STARI GRAD\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isto\\u010dni_Stari_Grad\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isto\\u010dni_Stari_Grad\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The significantly underdeveloped Municipality\", \"from\": 21, \"to\": 66}, {\"ngram\": \"Isto\\u010dni\", \"from\": 70, \"to\": 77}, {\"ngram\": \"Stari Grad\", \"from\": 78, \"to\": 88}, {\"ngram\": \"nearly 70 dunums\", \"from\": 101, \"to\": 117}, {\"ngram\": \"land\", \"from\": 121, \"to\": 125}, {\"ngram\": \"the \\\"Jahorina\\\" Olympic Centre\", \"from\": 153, \"to\": 182}, {\"ngram\": \"the construction\", \"from\": 187, \"to\": 203}, {\"ngram\": \"the largest toboggan run\", \"from\": 208, \"to\": 232}, {\"ngram\": \"the Balkans\", \"from\": 236, \"to\": 247}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They will allow the clearing of first and second-class forests and provide an additional million BAM from the citizens of this municipality to \\\"support\\\" the construction of the toboggan run.\", \"from\": 250, \"to\": 440, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the clearing\", \"from\": 266, \"to\": 278}, {\"ngram\": \"first and second-class forests\", \"from\": 282, \"to\": 312}, {\"ngram\": \"an additional million BAM\", \"from\": 325, \"to\": 350}, {\"ngram\": \"the citizens\", \"from\": 356, \"to\": 368}, {\"ngram\": \"this municipality\", \"from\": 372, \"to\": 389}, {\"ngram\": \"the construction\", \"from\": 403, \"to\": 419}, {\"ngram\": \"the toboggan run\", \"from\": 423, \"to\": 439}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This move continues the sale of Trebevi\\u0107 Mountain towards its eventual destruction, with entities, municipalities, and various political factions collaborating effectively in this effort.\", \"from\": 441, \"to\": 628, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 473, \"end\": 481, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trebevi\\u0107\", \"score\": 0.961342827547572, \"rank\": 0.04021164021163416, \"text\": \"Trebevi\\u0107\", \"types\": [\"Q473972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trebevi\\u0107\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trebevi\\u0107\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This move\", \"from\": 441, \"to\": 450}, {\"ngram\": \"the sale\", \"from\": 461, \"to\": 469}, {\"ngram\": \"its eventual destruction\", \"from\": 499, \"to\": 523}, {\"ngram\": \"entities\", \"from\": 530, \"to\": 538}, {\"ngram\": \"municipalities\", \"from\": 540, \"to\": 554}, {\"ngram\": \"various political factions\", \"from\": 560, \"to\": 586}, {\"ngram\": \"this effort\", \"from\": 616, \"to\": 627}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As for the citizens, they are left without even clean air.\", \"from\": 629, \"to\": 687, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the citizens\", \"from\": 636, \"to\": 648}, {\"ngram\": \"even clean air\", \"from\": 672, \"to\": 686}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Late last year, the Assembly of the Municipality of Isto\\u010dni Stari Grad adopted a Decision on determining an investment project of special interest for this municipality, which concerns the construction of the largest toboggan run or ski resort in the Balkans.\", \"from\": 689, \"to\": 948, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Assembly\", \"from\": 705, \"to\": 717}, {\"ngram\": \"the Municipality\", \"from\": 721, \"to\": 737}, {\"ngram\": \"Isto\\u010dni\", \"from\": 741, \"to\": 748}, {\"ngram\": \"Stari Grad\", \"from\": 749, \"to\": 759}, {\"ngram\": \"a Decision\", \"from\": 768, \"to\": 778}, {\"ngram\": \"an investment project\", \"from\": 794, \"to\": 815}, {\"ngram\": \"special interest\", \"from\": 819, \"to\": 835}, {\"ngram\": \"this municipality\", \"from\": 840, \"to\": 857}, {\"ngram\": \"the construction\", \"from\": 874, \"to\": 890}, {\"ngram\": \"the largest toboggan run\", \"from\": 894, \"to\": 918}, {\"ngram\": \"ski resort\", \"from\": 922, \"to\": 932}, {\"ngram\": \"the Balkans\", \"from\": 936, \"to\": 947}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Thus, they donated almost 70 dunums, specifically 69,763 square metres of land owned by the municipality, to the \\\"Jahorina\\\" Olympic Centre without any compensation.\", \"from\": 950, \"to\": 1114, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"almost 70 dunums\", \"from\": 969, \"to\": 985}, {\"ngram\": \"specifically 69,763 square metres\", \"from\": 987, \"to\": 1020}, {\"ngram\": \"land\", \"from\": 1024, \"to\": 1028}, {\"ngram\": \"the municipality\", \"from\": 1038, \"to\": 1054}, {\"ngram\": \"the \\\"Jahorina\\\" Olympic Centre\", \"from\": 1059, \"to\": 1088}, {\"ngram\": \"any compensation\", \"from\": 1097, \"to\": 1113}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The value of the real estate being transferred, which includes the land and infrastructure, amounts to three million BAM.\", \"from\": 1116, \"to\": 1237, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The value\", \"from\": 1116, \"to\": 1125}, {\"ngram\": \"the real estate\", \"from\": 1129, \"to\": 1144}, {\"ngram\": \"the land\", \"from\": 1179, \"to\": 1187}, {\"ngram\": \"infrastructure\", \"from\": 1192, \"to\": 1206}, {\"ngram\": \"three million BAM\", \"from\": 1219, \"to\": 1236}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The value of the investment project is 11 million BAM, of which \\\"Jahorina\\\" Olympic Centre is obliged to allocate ten million, while the Municipality of Isto\\u010dni Stari Grad, in addition to losing land worth three million, will provide another million BAM for the toboggan run, which has not yet even started.\", \"from\": 1238, \"to\": 1544, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The value\", \"from\": 1238, \"to\": 1247}, {\"ngram\": \"the investment project\", \"from\": 1251, \"to\": 1273}, {\"ngram\": \"11 million BAM\", \"from\": 1277, \"to\": 1291}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"Jahorina\\\" Olympic Centre\", \"from\": 1302, \"to\": 1327}, {\"ngram\": \"the Municipality\", \"from\": 1370, \"to\": 1386}, {\"ngram\": \"Isto\\u010dni\", \"from\": 1390, \"to\": 1397}, {\"ngram\": \"Stari Grad\", \"from\": 1398, \"to\": 1408}, {\"ngram\": \"addition\", \"from\": 1413, \"to\": 1421}, {\"ngram\": \"land\", \"from\": 1432, \"to\": 1436}, {\"ngram\": \"another million BAM\", \"from\": 1471, \"to\": 1490}, {\"ngram\": \"the toboggan run\", \"from\": 1495, \"to\": 1511}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Therefore, the total amount that will benefit the Olympic Center Jahorina is four million, while the total budget of this municipality is barely five million.\", \"from\": 1545, \"to\": 1703, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the total amount\", \"from\": 1556, \"to\": 1572}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Center Jahorina\", \"from\": 1591, \"to\": 1618}, {\"ngram\": \"the total budget\", \"from\": 1642, \"to\": 1658}, {\"ngram\": \"this municipality\", \"from\": 1662, \"to\": 1679}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To expedite the transfer of 1/1 land ownership to the \\\"Jahorina\\\" Olympic Centre, the officials from this municipality continually justified it by citing a \\\"special interest for the municipality\\\", and the decision came into effect immediately upon adoption.\", \"from\": 1705, \"to\": 1961, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the transfer\", \"from\": 1717, \"to\": 1729}, {\"ngram\": \"1/1 land ownership\", \"from\": 1733, \"to\": 1751}, {\"ngram\": \"the \\\"Jahorina\\\" Olympic Centre\", \"from\": 1755, \"to\": 1784}, {\"ngram\": \"the officials\", \"from\": 1786, \"to\": 1799}, {\"ngram\": \"this municipality\", \"from\": 1805, \"to\": 1822}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\\"special interest\", \"from\": 1858, \"to\": 1877}, {\"ngram\": \"the municipality\", \"from\": 1882, \"to\": 1898}, {\"ngram\": \"the decision\", \"from\": 1905, \"to\": 1917}, {\"ngram\": \"effect\", \"from\": 1928, \"to\": 1934}, {\"ngram\": \"adoption\", \"from\": 1952, \"to\": 1960}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The special interest of this point lies in the justified need to enhance the tourist offerings on Trebevi\\u0107, and it is considered that the construction of the most modern toboggan run (ski resort) in the Balkans is a project of crucial importance for the Municipality of Isto\\u010dni Stari Grad, but also for the City of Isto\\u010dno Sarajevo\\\", the Decision states.\", \"from\": 1963, \"to\": 2318, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2062, \"end\": 2070, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trebevi\\u0107\", \"score\": 0.9466040856134769, \"rank\": 0.04021164021163416, \"text\": \"Trebevi\\u0107\", \"types\": [\"Q473972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trebevi\\u0107\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trebevi\\u0107\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The special interest\", \"from\": 1964, \"to\": 1984}, {\"ngram\": \"this point\", \"from\": 1988, \"to\": 1998}, {\"ngram\": \"the justified need\", \"from\": 2007, \"to\": 2025}, {\"ngram\": \"the tourist offerings\", \"from\": 2037, \"to\": 2058}, {\"ngram\": \"the construction\", \"from\": 2098, \"to\": 2114}, {\"ngram\": \"the most modern toboggan run\", \"from\": 2118, \"to\": 2146}, {\"ngram\": \"ski resort\", \"from\": 2148, \"to\": 2158}, {\"ngram\": \"the Balkans\", \"from\": 2163, \"to\": 2174}, {\"ngram\": \"a project\", \"from\": 2178, \"to\": 2187}, {\"ngram\": \"crucial importance\", \"from\": 2191, \"to\": 2209}, {\"ngram\": \"the Municipality\", \"from\": 2214, \"to\": 2230}, {\"ngram\": \"Isto\\u010dni\", \"from\": 2234, \"to\": 2241}, {\"ngram\": \"Stari Grad\", \"from\": 2242, \"to\": 2252}, {\"ngram\": \"the City\", \"from\": 2267, \"to\": 2275}, {\"ngram\": \"Isto\\u010dno Sarajevo\", \"from\": 2279, \"to\": 2295}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\", the Decision states\", \"from\": 2295, \"to\": 2317}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, the basis on which this municipality assessed that it is in their interest to increase the profit of the \\\"Jahorina\\\" Olympic Centre and certain individuals, rather than working to increase their own budget, has not been validly explained anywhere.\", \"from\": 2320, \"to\": 2575, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the basis\", \"from\": 2329, \"to\": 2338}, {\"ngram\": \"this municipality\", \"from\": 2348, \"to\": 2365}, {\"ngram\": \"their interest\", \"from\": 2389, \"to\": 2403}, {\"ngram\": \"the profit\", \"from\": 2416, \"to\": 2426}, {\"ngram\": \"the \\\"Jahorina\\\" Olympic Centre\", \"from\": 2430, \"to\": 2459}, {\"ngram\": \"certain individuals\", \"from\": 2464, \"to\": 2483}, {\"ngram\": \"their own budget\", \"from\": 2517, \"to\": 2533}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Attorney Din Te\\u0161i\\u0107 told SPIN info that there must be some act confirming that such a decision by the Municipal Assembly is indeed of public interest.\", \"from\": 2577, \"to\": 2726, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2688, \"end\": 2696, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Deliberative_assembly\", \"score\": 0.999999999661668, \"rank\": 3.3814946112578924e-10, \"text\": \"Assembly\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Deliberative_assembly\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Deliberative_assembly\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Attorney Din Te\\u0161i\\u0107\", \"from\": 2577, \"to\": 2595}, {\"ngram\": \"SPIN info\", \"from\": 2601, \"to\": 2610}, {\"ngram\": \"some act\", \"from\": 2630, \"to\": 2638}, {\"ngram\": \"such a decision\", \"from\": 2655, \"to\": 2670}, {\"ngram\": \"public interest\", \"from\": 2710, \"to\": 2725}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This act must be clearly explained and factually supported.\", \"from\": 2727, \"to\": 2786, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This act\", \"from\": 2727, \"to\": 2735}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Furthermore, between commercial entities, the possibility of gifting is not legally foreseen.\", \"from\": 2787, \"to\": 2880, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"commercial entities\", \"from\": 2808, \"to\": 2827}, {\"ngram\": \"the possibility\", \"from\": 2829, \"to\": 2844}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The Prosecutor's Office should review this type of contract because they had the option to convert their capital into shares and become co-owners to some extent.\", \"from\": 2882, \"to\": 3044, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Prosecutor's Office\", \"from\": 2883, \"to\": 2906}, {\"ngram\": \"this type\", \"from\": 2921, \"to\": 2930}, {\"ngram\": \"contract\", \"from\": 2934, \"to\": 2942}, {\"ngram\": \"the option\", \"from\": 2960, \"to\": 2970}, {\"ngram\": \"their capital\", \"from\": 2982, \"to\": 2995}, {\"ngram\": \"shares\", \"from\": 3001, \"to\": 3007}, {\"ngram\": \"co\", \"from\": 3019, \"to\": 3021}, {\"ngram\": \"owners\", \"from\": 3022, \"to\": 3028}, {\"ngram\": \"some extent\", \"from\": 3032, \"to\": 3043}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This way, they would have dividends, achieve their goals, and have the ability to manage the ski resort.\", \"from\": 3045, \"to\": 3149, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"dividends\", \"from\": 3071, \"to\": 3080}, {\"ngram\": \"their goals\", \"from\": 3090, \"to\": 3101}, {\"ngram\": \"the ability\", \"from\": 3112, \"to\": 3123}, {\"ngram\": \"the ski resort\", \"from\": 3134, \"to\": 3148}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is the only lawful and legally valid solution in the interest of the municipality.\", \"from\": 3150, \"to\": 3237, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the only lawful and legally valid solution\", \"from\": 3158, \"to\": 3200}, {\"ngram\": \"the interest\", \"from\": 3204, \"to\": 3216}, {\"ngram\": \"the municipality\", \"from\": 3220, \"to\": 3236}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the manner it was done, we come to a transfer of ownership without compensation, a payment of one million BAM, all of which goes to some shareholders' ownership for them to enrich themselves, without clearly defined economic parametres.\", \"from\": 3238, \"to\": 3477, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the manner\", \"from\": 3241, \"to\": 3251}, {\"ngram\": \"a transfer\", \"from\": 3276, \"to\": 3286}, {\"ngram\": \"ownership\", \"from\": 3290, \"to\": 3299}, {\"ngram\": \"compensation\", \"from\": 3308, \"to\": 3320}, {\"ngram\": \"a payment\", \"from\": 3322, \"to\": 3331}, {\"ngram\": \"one million BAM\", \"from\": 3335, \"to\": 3350}, {\"ngram\": \"some shareholders' ownership\", \"from\": 3373, \"to\": 3401}, {\"ngram\": \"clearly defined economic parametres\", \"from\": 3441, \"to\": 3476}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is certain that the Municipality of Isto\\u010dni Stari Grad and the City of Isto\\u010dno Sarajevo would have had far greater benefits if they had become co-owners, where they could also control the way the operations are conducted\\\",says Te\\u0161i\\u0107, emphasizing that the municipality has been harmed in this manner and that the competent prosecutor's office should consider whether it is a criminal act and possibly initiate an investigation.\", \"from\": 3478, \"to\": 3907, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Municipality\", \"from\": 3497, \"to\": 3513}, {\"ngram\": \"Isto\\u010dni\", \"from\": 3517, \"to\": 3524}, {\"ngram\": \"Stari Grad\", \"from\": 3525, \"to\": 3535}, {\"ngram\": \"the City\", \"from\": 3540, \"to\": 3548}, {\"ngram\": \"Isto\\u010dno Sarajevo\", \"from\": 3552, \"to\": 3568}, {\"ngram\": \"far greater benefits\", \"from\": 3584, \"to\": 3604}, {\"ngram\": \"co\", \"from\": 3624, \"to\": 3626}, {\"ngram\": \"owners\", \"from\": 3627, \"to\": 3633}, {\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 3665, \"to\": 3672}, {\"ngram\": \"the operations\", \"from\": 3673, \"to\": 3687}, {\"ngram\": \"the municipality\", \"from\": 3732, \"to\": 3748}, {\"ngram\": \"this manner\", \"from\": 3768, \"to\": 3779}, {\"ngram\": \"the competent prosecutor's office\", \"from\": 3789, \"to\": 3822}, {\"ngram\": \"a criminal act\", \"from\": 3853, \"to\": 3867}, {\"ngram\": \"an investigation\", \"from\": 3890, \"to\": 3906}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Within the 69,763 square metres of land that will be transferred to the \\\"Jahorina\\\" Olympic Centre without compensation, there are 7,090 square metres of first and second-class forests that will be cleared.\", \"from\": 3909, \"to\": 4114, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 69,763 square metres\", \"from\": 3916, \"to\": 3940}, {\"ngram\": \"land\", \"from\": 3944, \"to\": 3948}, {\"ngram\": \"the \\\"Jahorina\\\" Olympic Centre\", \"from\": 3977, \"to\": 4006}, {\"ngram\": \"compensation\", \"from\": 4015, \"to\": 4027}, {\"ngram\": \"7,090 square metres\", \"from\": 4039, \"to\": 4058}, {\"ngram\": \"first and second-class forests\", \"from\": 4062, \"to\": 4092}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Since the ownership of the land in question has changed, the new owner is obligated to bear all costs of the further forest clearing process and changing the purpose of the forest land.\", \"from\": 4116, \"to\": 4302, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the ownership\", \"from\": 4123, \"to\": 4136}, {\"ngram\": \"the land\", \"from\": 4140, \"to\": 4148}, {\"ngram\": \"question\", \"from\": 4152, \"to\": 4160}, {\"ngram\": \"the new owner\", \"from\": 4174, \"to\": 4187}, {\"ngram\": \"all costs\", \"from\": 4209, \"to\": 4218}, {\"ngram\": \"the further forest clearing process\", \"from\": 4222, \"to\": 4257}, {\"ngram\": \"the purpose\", \"from\": 4271, \"to\": 4282}, {\"ngram\": \"the forest land\", \"from\": 4286, \"to\": 4301}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The resulting assortments belong to the Public Enterprise 'Forests of RS' a.d. Sokolac\\\", the Decision states.\", \"from\": 4303, \"to\": 4412, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The resulting assortments\", \"from\": 4303, \"to\": 4328}, {\"ngram\": \"the Public Enterprise 'Forests\", \"from\": 4339, \"to\": 4369}, {\"ngram\": \"RS' a.d. Sokolac\", \"from\": 4373, \"to\": 4389}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Trebevi\\u0107 was protected as a park forest with special features back in 1954.\", \"from\": 4414, \"to\": 4489, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Trebevi\\u0107\", \"from\": 4414, \"to\": 4422}, {\"ngram\": \"a park forest\", \"from\": 4440, \"to\": 4453}, {\"ngram\": \"special features\", \"from\": 4459, \"to\": 4475}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Although the City of Isto\\u010dno Sarajevo declared part of Trebevi\\u0107 a Nature Park a few years ago, during the presentation of the Protection Study prepared by the Republic Institute for the Protection of Cultural, Historical, and Natural Heritage, it was stated that the forest would not be cut, UNLESS someone deems it necessary\\u2026 which leaves the possibility of uncontrolled logging, a significant problem in Bosnia and Herzegovina.\", \"from\": 4490, \"to\": 4919, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the City\", \"from\": 4499, \"to\": 4507}, {\"ngram\": \"Isto\\u010dno Sarajevo\", \"from\": 4511, \"to\": 4527}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 4537, \"to\": 4541}, {\"ngram\": \"Trebevi\\u0107\", \"from\": 4545, \"to\": 4553}, {\"ngram\": \"a Nature Park\", \"from\": 4554, \"to\": 4567}, {\"ngram\": \"the presentation\", \"from\": 4592, \"to\": 4608}, {\"ngram\": \"the Protection Study\", \"from\": 4612, \"to\": 4632}, {\"ngram\": \"the Republic Institute\", \"from\": 4645, \"to\": 4667}, {\"ngram\": \"the Protection\", \"from\": 4672, \"to\": 4686}, {\"ngram\": \"Cultural\", \"from\": 4690, \"to\": 4698}, {\"ngram\": \"Historical\", \"from\": 4700, \"to\": 4710}, {\"ngram\": \"Natural Heritage\", \"from\": 4716, \"to\": 4732}, {\"ngram\": \"the forest\", \"from\": 4753, \"to\": 4763}, {\"ngram\": \"someone\", \"from\": 4789, \"to\": 4796}, {\"ngram\": \"the possibility\", \"from\": 4830, \"to\": 4845}, {\"ngram\": \"uncontrolled logging\", \"from\": 4849, \"to\": 4869}, {\"ngram\": \"a significant problem\", \"from\": 4871, \"to\": 4892}, {\"ngram\": \"Bosnia\", \"from\": 4896, \"to\": 4902}, {\"ngram\": \"Herzegovina\", \"from\": 4907, \"to\": 4918}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Azra Berbi\\u0107, an activist from the Foundation Atelier for Social Changes - ACT, believes that such a decision by the local authorities will lead to a reduction in forest areas and that it is more important to make decisions that protect this green treasure.\", \"from\": 4921, \"to\": 5177, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Azra Berbi\\u0107\", \"from\": 4921, \"to\": 4932}, {\"ngram\": \"an activist\", \"from\": 4934, \"to\": 4945}, {\"ngram\": \"the Foundation Atelier\", \"from\": 4951, \"to\": 4973}, {\"ngram\": \"Social Changes - ACT\", \"from\": 4978, \"to\": 4998}, {\"ngram\": \"such a decision\", \"from\": 5014, \"to\": 5029}, {\"ngram\": \"the local authorities\", \"from\": 5033, \"to\": 5054}, {\"ngram\": \"a reduction\", \"from\": 5068, \"to\": 5079}, {\"ngram\": \"forest areas\", \"from\": 5083, \"to\": 5095}, {\"ngram\": \"decisions\", \"from\": 5134, \"to\": 5143}, {\"ngram\": \"this green treasure\", \"from\": 5157, \"to\": 5176}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Azra questions whether this decision truly satisfies the public interest, considering the consequences of the climate crisis we witness year after year.\", \"from\": 5178, \"to\": 5330, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Azra questions\", \"from\": 5178, \"to\": 5192}, {\"ngram\": \"this decision\", \"from\": 5201, \"to\": 5214}, {\"ngram\": \"the public interest\", \"from\": 5231, \"to\": 5250}, {\"ngram\": \"the consequences\", \"from\": 5264, \"to\": 5280}, {\"ngram\": \"the climate crisis\", \"from\": 5284, \"to\": 5302}, {\"ngram\": \"year\", \"from\": 5325, \"to\": 5329}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Additionally, it is important to note that this action violates the Law on the Temporary Prohibition of Disposal of State Property in Bosnia and Herzegovina, given that the forests are state-owned, as confirmed by the Constitutional Court of BiH in its decision, which states that 'state ownership can also include public goods that by their nature primarily serve all people, such as running water, forests, and state infrastructure networks in the sense of Annex 9 of the General Framework Agreement for Peace in BiH, etc.'\\\".\", \"from\": 5332, \"to\": 5860, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this action\", \"from\": 5376, \"to\": 5387}, {\"ngram\": \"the Law\", \"from\": 5397, \"to\": 5404}, {\"ngram\": \"the Temporary Prohibition\", \"from\": 5408, \"to\": 5433}, {\"ngram\": \"Disposal\", \"from\": 5437, \"to\": 5445}, {\"ngram\": \"State Property\", \"from\": 5449, \"to\": 5463}, {\"ngram\": \"Bosnia\", \"from\": 5467, \"to\": 5473}, {\"ngram\": \"Herzegovina\", \"from\": 5478, \"to\": 5489}, {\"ngram\": \"the forests\", \"from\": 5502, \"to\": 5513}, {\"ngram\": \"the Constitutional Court\", \"from\": 5547, \"to\": 5571}, {\"ngram\": \"BiH\", \"from\": 5575, \"to\": 5578}, {\"ngram\": \"its decision\", \"from\": 5582, \"to\": 5594}, {\"ngram\": \"state ownership\", \"from\": 5615, \"to\": 5630}, {\"ngram\": \"public goods\", \"from\": 5648, \"to\": 5660}, {\"ngram\": \"their nature\", \"from\": 5669, \"to\": 5681}, {\"ngram\": \"all people\", \"from\": 5698, \"to\": 5708}, {\"ngram\": \"running water\", \"from\": 5718, \"to\": 5731}, {\"ngram\": \"forests\", \"from\": 5733, \"to\": 5740}, {\"ngram\": \"state infrastructure networks\", \"from\": 5746, \"to\": 5775}, {\"ngram\": \"the sense\", \"from\": 5779, \"to\": 5788}, {\"ngram\": \"Annex\", \"from\": 5792, \"to\": 5797}, {\"ngram\": \"the General Framework Agreement\", \"from\": 5803, \"to\": 5834}, {\"ngram\": 