\": 6326, \"to\": 6339}, {\"ngram\": \"the winter ski season\", \"from\": 6373, \"to\": 6394}, {\"ngram\": \"this sector\", \"from\": 6403, \"to\": 6414}, {\"ngram\": \"tourism\", \"from\": 6418, \"to\": 6425}, {\"ngram\": \"our country\", \"from\": 6429, \"to\": 6440}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The question arises, what is more important at this moment: preserving seven dunums of high-value forest or building a toboggan run that soon may not have enough snow during the winter season?\", \"from\": 6462, \"to\": 6654, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The question\", \"from\": 6462, \"to\": 6474}, {\"ngram\": \"this moment\", \"from\": 6509, \"to\": 6520}, {\"ngram\": \"seven dunums\", \"from\": 6533, \"to\": 6545}, {\"ngram\": \"high-value forest\", \"from\": 6549, \"to\": 6566}, {\"ngram\": \"a toboggan run\", \"from\": 6579, \"to\": 6593}, {\"ngram\": \"enough snow\", \"from\": 6617, \"to\": 6628}, {\"ngram\": \"the winter season\", \"from\": 6636, \"to\": 6653}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"says Azra Berbi\\u0107 to SPIN Info.\", \"from\": 6654, \"to\": 6685, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6660, \"end\": 6664, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Azra\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.3077270278400078e-27, \"text\": \"Azra\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q215380\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Azra\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Azra\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"SPIN Info\", \"from\": 6675, \"to\": 6684}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ironically, on some of the buildings currently under construction on Trebevi\\u0107, there is a sign that reads: \\\"Clean air has no price\\\".\", \"from\": 6687, \"to\": 6820, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6756, \"end\": 6764, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trebevi\\u0107\", \"score\": 0.9466040856134769, \"rank\": 0.04021164021163416, \"text\": \"Trebevi\\u0107\", \"types\": [\"Q473972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trebevi\\u0107\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/res